  "name": "Goo Grenade (Major)",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> Strike</p>\n<p>A goo grenade is a flask filled with a fast-growing, short-lived alchemical ooze. When you hit a creature with a goo grenade, that creature takes 4d4 acid damage, 4 persistent acid damage, and 4 acid splash damage, and a -10 circumstance penalty to its Speeds from the clinging goo. You gain a +3 item bonus to attack rolls. The target can end any penalties, conditions, and persistent damage caused by the bomb by Escaping (DC 35) or spending a total of 3 Interact actions to pry themselves free of the ooze. These Interact actions don't have to be consecutive, and other creatures can provide the actions as well.</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-effects.Item.5JYchreCttBg7RcD]{Effect: Goo Grenade}</p>"
